    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/d4caaae664d885a5b2c1c107cdc5a7c1.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>SUMMARY</strong><br><br>A slice of life boys love visual novel about experiencing childhood, adolescence, and adulthood.<br>While visiting a small town during the summer holiday, Henry meets two older boys named Jason and Eddie. The three hang out daily, and Henry starts seeing them as his older brothers. Henry has to say goodbye to his friends when the holiday ends, but they will reunite another summer.<br><br><strong>Love Interests</strong><br>Eddie and Jason are the only two love interests. Eddie acts as the smart and gentle older brother and Jason acts as the cool and playful older brother. They treat Henry as their little brother at first, but as they grow older, they might see him in a more romantic way.<br>Whether you want a friendship ending, a romance ending, a poly ending, or a breakup ending, anything is possible.<br><br><strong>Childhood</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/7f48ab7142f9d43a541cdac35704178e.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Adolescence</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/b7bb3a4e28987dea5293742cac7e1255.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Adulthood</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/708db3a7a640ed39b8d94d7b05f80457.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Meet the Townsfolk</strong><br>Talk to the townsfolk and see their events! If you see 9 of their events and max out their friendship, something might happen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/b8a2aa8d86af529ed1410d4b361b1f01.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Points</strong><br>Affection will increase by choosing the right choices. Bond will increase by spending time with the townsfolk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/f54270c6f708e199a0999b9c24dd4b2f.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Hangout Event</strong><br>Seeing limited hangout events will strengthen your relationships!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/1c1d30c8ca23c45ea48a1474d67d4a5a.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Shop</strong><br>You can give gifts to increase affection. Each item has a different function.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/47b3bcfbdbb13d15a0765a8fdfe31fa3.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Explore the Town</strong><br>Every day, you will get an opportunity to visit the townsfolk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/fdc51ed7dc7c69a8ada2ea4f3b05dfb8.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>Stats</strong><br>Raise stats in order to improve your chances of spending time with the Love Interests.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265270/extras/f6593b210a8859748f340560b1f480e1.avif?t=1682096772\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br>- 63K Words (Around 5 Hours Playtime)<br>- 24 CGs<br>- 5 Friendship Routes (9 Hangout Events Each)<br>- 2 Love Interests (Includes Neutral Ending, Romance Ending, Poly Ending, and Breakup Ending)",
